title: Mitch McConnell
added: With the election victories of Democrats [[Raphael Warnock]] and [[Jon Ossoff]] in both a [[2020-21 United States Senate special election in Georgia|special]] and [[2020-21 United States Senate election in Georgia|regular]] election in [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]], respectively, McConnell is expected to return to the position of minority leader, as both Democrats' victories ensured a 50-50 tie in the Senate, which can be broken by [[Vice President of the United States|Vice President]]-elect [[Kamala Harris]].
